{"tid":735021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國關稅豁免只限「產品無法從中國境外獲得」的美國企業申請","createTime":"2018-07-09T06:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T06:57:22.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"88873edca53ea6f0af7bc9ba7e2e711d04f800e3","tid":735021,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:57:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280709237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN280709237&d=o3r6j3M7AqXltrNppPm1YcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a1792b20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280709237</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280709237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Deditorchoice%26newsid%3DETN280709237&d=o3r6j3M7AqXltrNppPm1YcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=a1792b20\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=editorchoice&amp;newsid=ETN280709237</a><br />\n<br />\n《經濟通通訊社９日專訊》美國貿易代表辦公室（ＵＳＴＲ）表示，在美國對進口中國商品加徵關稅中受影響的企業，可以有９０日的時間申請豁免，豁免期限為一年。<br />\n<br />\n　　上周美國對價值３４０億美元的中國出口產品徵收新關稅，ＵＳＴＲ表示，如果關稅對企業造成嚴重的經濟損害，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兼且相關產品無法從中國境外獲得</span></span></strong>，受影響的公司可申請關稅豁免，申請期將於１０月９日截止。"}]}